snippet.title: PlayStation All-Stars Battle Royale - Zeus Trailer
snippet.description:
PlayStation® All-Stars Battle Royale™ is free-for-all brawler featuring the greatest stars in the PlayStation universe! Zeus - the King of the Gods, Ruler of Mount Olympus, and God of Thunder joins the battle!
